{"TopicId":184398,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Instantly cut thrust","CreatedByName":"ExMauler","CreatedById":152550,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T04:07:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"ExMauler","CreatedById":152550,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T04:07:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am a Kerbal fan from WAY back but have been absent awhile, trying to re-orient myself. There is a mod or a tweak that allows for instant thrust cut, i.e. you press X and the engines stop. Any help please and thank you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T04:13:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223597114\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184398\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557547650\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152550\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ExMauler\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, ExMauler said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni.e. you press X and the engines stop.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nErrr..... You press X and the engines stop.\u00A0 (I\u0027m 99% sure this is stock)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SRB","CreatedById":197002,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T04:14:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m pretty sure that exists in stock KSP\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ExMauler","CreatedById":152550,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T04:20:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223597117\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184398\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557548030\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nErrr..... You press X and the engines stop.\u00A0 (I\u0027m 99% sure this is stock)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks but no. there is a tweak or a mod that allows for INSTANT engine stop. With most engines you press X and it slows quickly but still gradually.\u00A0 No what i mean?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kryxal","CreatedById":102688,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T04:22:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLikewise, Z turns the engines on at 100%, though that functionality wasn\u0027t always there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T04:29:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223597123\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184398\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557548454\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152550\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ExMauler\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, ExMauler said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks but no. there is a tweak or a mod that allows for INSTANT engine stop. With most engines you press X and it slows quickly but still gradually.\u00A0 No what i mean?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nErr, no, cause when I hit X, my engines stop.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ExMauler","CreatedById":152550,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T04:30:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know how to explain this anymore succinctly. It\u0027s like a light switch, you flip the switch the light instantly ceases to be. In KSP stock you press X, there is a lag.\u003Cbr\u003E\nBut there is a tweak that allows for a \u0022light switch\u0022 type option to cut thrust instantly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T04:43:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHello \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/152550-exmauler/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022152550\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/152550-exmauler/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@ExMauler\u003C/a\u003E, do you mean you are having trouble when trying to burn for an intercept? If so the method I use is to get close to the end of my burn, press x, then use shift to apply a small amount of thrust for precision intercepts. Sometimes I right click on the engine and lower the thrust to 1% (usually when I\u0027m trying to match orbits for RV or docking).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf not a mod like Kerbal Operating System (KOS) allows you to program your rocket:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9650944194\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/165628-17-kos-v1180-kos-scriptable-autopilot-system/\u0026amp;tab=comments\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=3175111\u0026amp;embedComment=3175111\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment#comment-3175111\u0022 style=\u0022height:309px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"4x4cheesecake","CreatedById":187982,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T04:59:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you use a clean install or did you upgrad from a previous (pretty early) version? If it is the latter case, maybe the keybindings are not updated properly, I would suggest to check them manually. The option is called \u0022Throttle cut-off\u0022 and can be found in Settings -\u0026gt; Input -\u0026gt; Vessel:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022JNYYsAg.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/JNYYsAg.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-11T04:59:56Z\u0022 title=\u002205/11/2019 04:59  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 11, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by 4x4cheesecake\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ExMauler","CreatedById":152550,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T05:22:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJames kerman, Thank you but again, no. When I played KSP a few years ago I had a mod (or tweak) that allowed for instant shut off of engines when pressing X. The norm is that you press X and the engines shut down but there is a bit of a lag (they shutdown slowly). This mod/tweak shut them down instantly like a light switch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fulgur","CreatedById":195204,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T05:28:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou mean like a jet engine?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ExMauler","CreatedById":152550,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T06:27:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI give up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OHara","CreatedById":162784,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T06:44:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith default keybindings, for engines other than jet engines, in stock KSP the \u0027X\u0027 key does turn off the thrust like a light switch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust in case anyone else who finds this thread later, *is* looking for how to make jet engines respond instantly, there is a configuration variable for that, so ModuleManager can make the change, with this in a configuration\u00A0file\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003E@PART[*]:HAS[@MODULE[ModuleEnginesFX]] {\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0@MODULE[ModuleEnginesFX],* {\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0 \u00A0 \u00A0 \u00A0@engineDecelerationSpeed = 1e6\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003E}}\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nor to remove both the spooling up and spooling down entirely\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003E@PART[*]:HAS[@MODULE[ModuleEnginesFX]] {\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\u00A0 \u00A0@MODULE[ModuleEnginesFX],* {\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0 \u00A0 \u00A0 \u00A0!useEngineResponseTime = delete\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Courier New\u0027, Courier, monospace;\u0022\u003E}}\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-11T07:22:29Z\u0022 title=\u002205/11/2019 07:22  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 11, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by OHara\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Emore likely anyone finding this would want to remove spooling entirely\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Serenity","CreatedById":179192,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-11T09:01:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223597154\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184398\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557556079\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152550\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ExMauler\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, ExMauler said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI give up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe put the engines shutdown/toggle in an Action group like number 1 and hit it the moment you want them off.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt should help a bit more, havent tested it though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is also a great mod for putting action groups while in flight (if you dont want to launch the vessel again).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed2189486762\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/178733-15x-action-group-manager-renewed/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:225px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-05-11T09:06:29Z\u0022 title=\u002205/11/2019 09:06  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EMay 11, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Boyster\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Adenosine Triphospate","CreatedById":197303,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-12T09:10:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223597154\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184398\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557556079\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152550\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ExMauler\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/11/2019 at 7:27 AM, ExMauler said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI give up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you using a jet engine? Jet engines naturally slowly diminish their thrust, several seconds after pressing X. Theres not way to avoid that, I\u0027m afraid.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fourfa","CreatedById":151713,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-05-15T01:51:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223597671\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022184398\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221557652233\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197303\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Adenosine Triphospate\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/12/2019 at 2:10 AM, Adenosine Triphospate said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre you using a jet engine? Jet engines naturally slowly diminish their thrust, several seconds after pressing X. Theres not way to avoid that, I\u0027m afraid.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is, actually...\u00A0 Read the text at the following Imgur album:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/a/qh6av\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com/a/qh6av\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks to \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/50750-azimech/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002250750\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/50750-azimech/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Azimech\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0for putting this together\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}